      "text": "After Adam (peace and blessings be upon him), Allah blessed the descendants of Adam, his children and grandchildren, and they spread and multiplied. If Adam had come back and seen them all, and someone had said to him, 'These are your descendants, Adam,' he would have been astonished. He would have said, 'Glory be to Allah! These are all my children! These are all my descendants!'",
